{"tid":2408361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬甸「封網」前夕軍車入仰光  北部城市開槍放催淚彈  記者直播被拘","createTime":"2021-02-15T00:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T00:37:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d0823c48c9d779eb0bbad6c64c4aa9d51bd7cace","tid":2408361,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T00:36:43.000Z","msg":"緬甸「封網」前夕軍車入仰光 <br />\n北部城市開槍放催淚彈 <br />\n記者直播被拘<br />\nFeb 15, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vGCo_lc3y5o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvGCo_lc3y5o&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4efSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=28c2d98d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vGCo_lc3y5o</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n57.8K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n緬甸傳出周一凌晨1時至9時「禁網」，在一向平靜的最大城市仰光，周日下午及晚上開始有軍車入城，是自示威及戒嚴以來首次。<br />\n<br />\n美國、歐盟、德國、法國等多個西方國家駐緬甸大使在香港時間午夜發表聯合聲明，要求武裝部隊避免使用武力，及聲討軍方干擾通訊及限制緬甸人的基本自由。<br />\n<br />\n在北部城市密支那，網上片段顯示傳出多下槍聲，目前未知是否警員開橡膠子彈。當地警方又使用催淚彈驅散示威者。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒採訪期間，被要求停止直播；至少五名當地記者被扣押。"},{"pid":"52f292a39cf91e1aaf36741aa5db6052bc817d41","tid":2408361,"uid":275384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T00:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}